    "body": "possibly related to this issue, I'm seeing incorrect `up_to_date` status when adding an icon to the format: `up_to_date = '[✓](fg:iris)'`. With the default format of `up_to_date = ''`, there doesn't appear to be an issue while using the presets.\n\nThere was also a similar issue prior to PR [6476](https://github.com/starship/starship/pull/6476). The behavior prior to PR 6476 was that it would report incorrectly if there were just modified files. If there were modified and unstaged, then the prompt was correct.",
